CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780981448
OL,3,CCancer vaccine developed for people at
OL,4,Chight risk of disease
OL,6,FA vaccine designed for people at high
OL,7,Frisk of bowel and ovarian cancer has
OL,8,Fbeen developed by the University of
OL,9,FOxford alongside the pharmaceutical
OL,10,Ffirm Moderna.
OL,12,FExperts at Oxford believe the mRNA
OL,13,Ftechnology behind this vaccine has the
OL,14,Fpotential to be adapted for other
OL,15,Fcancers in the future.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
